@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Researcher Signs Up

actor Researcher
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
database "Database \n (Neon)" as DB

Researcher -> UI: Open 'Sign Up' page
Researcher -> UI: Fill registration form\nand submit
UI -> API: POST /signup (Researcher data)
API -> DB: Create new Researcher record
DB --> API: Success/Failure response
API --> UI: Return result (success/failure)
UI --> Researcher: Show confirmation or error

@enduml
